<body><div class=WordSection1>
<div class="brand">📚 ENGLISH CODING · 영어코딩</div>
<h1>⚙️ M002 Week 7 — Pistons</h1>
<p><strong>Topic:</strong> Pistons and Mazes · <strong>Course:</strong> Maze Madness · <strong>Level:</strong> Beginner · <strong>Time:</strong> about 25 minutes</p>
<p>A lever powers a piston. The piston opens a path. The agent crosses.</p>
<hr />
<h2>1 · Guess 🔮</h2>
<pre><code>move forward
interact ahead
move forward
</code></pre>
<p><strong>The agent flips the lever. The path opens. Can it cross? Circle one:</strong> yes · no</p>
<hr />
<h2>2 · Match 🔗</h2>
<p>Draw a line. Match each word to its meaning.</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Word</th>
<th>Meaning</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>lever</td>
<td>a hole in the floor</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>piston</td>
<td>you flip it ON or OFF</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>gap</td>
<td>it pushes a block</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<hr />
<h2>3 · Fill One Blank ✏️</h2>
<p>Flip the lever only at a gap. One word is missing.</p>
<pre><code>if ____ ahead:
    interact ahead
otherwise:
    move forward
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Missing word? Circle one:</strong> gap · grass · friend</p>
<hr />
<h2>4 · Show Your Work 📸🎥</h2>
<p>Open your homework world. Walk the agent to the lever. Flip it. Cross while the path is open. Reach the goal.</p>
<p>Record <strong>one video</strong> (a phone is fine). Show two things:</p>
<p><strong>1 · Your code.</strong> Scroll through it. Say what each part does.</p>
<p><strong>2 · Your build.</strong> Point the camera. Name the parts.</p>
<p>Fill the blanks:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Today I built ______.</p>
<p>I built it using this code: ______.</p>
<p>In this code I used ______.</p>
<p>The hardest part was ______.</p>
<p>That part was hard because ______.</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>Write your lines here, then say them in your video.</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<hr />
<h3>Submit ✅</h3>
<p>Send this worksheet + your video to teacher on KakaoTalk.</p>
